highlights.text: “Shape of You” by Ed Sheeran has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 131 weeks straight.
“I Think I'm OKAY (with YUNGBLUD & Travis Barker)” by Machine Gun Kelly, YUNGBLUD, and Travis Barker is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 96 spots at #76.
“Goodbyes (feat. Young Thug)” by Post Malone and Young Thug is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #2.
Ed Sheeran has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “I Don't Care (with Justin Bieber)” is the highest at #3.
